# ====================================
# üî• FIREBASE CONFIGURATION (REQUIRED)
# ====================================
# NyanProxy requires Firebase for persistent logging and user management
# Get these from Firebase Console ‚Üí Project Settings ‚Üí Service Accounts
#
# üîê PRIVACY NOTICE: Only usage metrics are logged, NOT prompt/response content
